# Paths excluded from clang-format (used by both the CLI and clangd/IDEs).
# Keep this list in sync with the CI format gate (.github/workflows/format.yaml).
#
# Vendored / upstream-derived code is excluded so that reformatting does not
# pollute future upstream-sync diffs:
#   - src/core/tomlc99: byte-for-byte cktan/tomlc99 (MIT).
#   - util: RTKLIB-derived utilities (BUILD_UTILS=OFF by default, never in the
#     v0.5.3 clang-format scope). See issue #166.
src/core/tomlc99/**
util/**
